snippet: Serena Williams may have been second best at the French Open on Saturday but the American has moved ahead of fellow tennis player Maria Sharapova to top the women's earnings list in sports, according to Forbes Magazine....
lead_paragraph: Serena Williams may have been second best at the French Open on Saturday but the American has moved ahead of fellow tennis player Maria Sharapova to top the women's earnings list in sports, according to Forbes Magazine.

headline.print_headline: Serena Passes Suspended Sharapova as Top Woman Earner
headline.main: Serena Passes Suspended Sharapova as Top Woman Earner
